        <p class="intro">
        <p>Paglaom Hostel offers budget travelers and surfers a clean and cozy place to stay with the lowest rates in General Luna, Siargao Island. It's the only hostel and free art accommodation on the island.</p>
        <a class="callout" href="#more">Find out more</a>
        
        <div class="wildlife">
        <h2>About Paglaom</h2>
      <p>
        For the cheap rate of PhP250 per person a night (5.5 USD) + 10 % tourist tax, guests can access to the following features: <a href="http://i2.wp.com/www.paglaomhostel.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/DSC3304.jpg?resize=640%2C320">A bed in one of our bunker beds sleeping halls</a>, <a href="http://i0.wp.com/www.paglaomhostel.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/DSC3111.jpg?resize=640%2C320">A mess hall area for kicking back</a>, and <a href="http://i0.wp.com/www.paglaomhostel.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/DSC3126.jpg?resize=640%2C320">A fully equipped kitchen for free usage</a>.
      </p>
			<a href="http://graph.facebook.com/373742319501502/picture">Find balance in life Have a great week, Paglaomers!</a>
